### Internova Backend API Test Suite
### Base URL: https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app

### =============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Register a new user
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "STUDENT",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "departmentId": "uuid-here"
}

### Login
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Get current user profile
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/me
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Refresh token
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/refresh
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Logout
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/logout
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### =============================================================================
### STUDENT ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Get student profile
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/students/profile
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Update student profile
PUT https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/students/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

{
  "course": "Computer Science",
  "cvUrl": "https://example.com/cv.pdf"
}

### Get profile completion
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/students/profile-completion
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### =============================================================================
### VACANCY ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Get all vacancies (public)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies?page=0&size=10

### Get vacancy by ID
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/{vacancy-id}

### Search vacancies
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/search?keyword=developer&page=0&size=10

### Get vacancy feed for department (student only)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/feed/{department-id}
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Post new vacancy (company only)
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

{
  "title": "Software Developer Intern",
  "description": "Great opportunity for students",
  "requirements": "Java, Spring Boot experience"
}

### Update vacancy (company owner only)
PUT https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/{vacancy-id}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "requirements": "Updated requirements"
}

### =============================================================================
### APPLICATION ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Apply to vacancy (student only)
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

{
  "vacancyId": "vacancy-uuid-here"
}

### Get my applications (student only)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications?page=0&size=10
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Get application by ID (student only)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications/{application-id}
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Withdraw application (student only)
DELETE https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications/{application-id}
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Update application status (company/admin only)
PATCH https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications/{application-id}/status?status=INTERVIEW
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### =============================================================================
### COMPANY ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Get company profile
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/company/profile
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Get company vacancies
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/company/vacancies
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Get verification status
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/company/verification-status
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### =============================================================================
### LOGBOOK ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Submit log entry (student only)
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/logbooks/submit?date=2024-03-19
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

{
  "content": "Worked on Spring Boot project, implemented authentication",
  "tags": "spring-boot,authentication,java"
}

### Get my log entries (student only)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/logbooks/my-logs
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### =============================================================================
### NOTIFICATION ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Get my notifications
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications?page=0&size=10
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Get unread count
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications/unread/count
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Mark notification as read
PATCH https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications/{notification-id}/read
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### Mark all notifications as read
PATCH https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications/read-all
Cookie: JWT=your-jwt-token-here

### =============================================================================
### HEALTH CHECK ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Application health check
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/actuator/health

### Application info
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/actuator/info

### =============================================================================
### TESTING INSTRUCTIONS
### =============================================================================
# 1. Start with authentication endpoints (register/login)
# 2. Use the JWT token from login response in Cookie header for authenticated requests
# 3. Test public endpoints first (vacancy listing)
# 4. Test role-specific endpoints based on user type
# 5. Check actuator endpoints for application health